有剩余可用的LVM的场景
1.查看剩余的空间
# pvs
  PV         VG    Fmt  Attr PSize   PFree  
  /dev/sda3  cpsVG lvm2 a--  931.03g 746.03g
2.查看LV
# lvs
data         VG -wi-ao---- 20.00g
3.扩展+100G
# lvm
lvm> lvextend -L +100G /dev/mapper/VG-data
  Extending logical volume image to 105.00 GiB
  Logical volume image successfully resized
4.更新文件系统
# resize2fs /dev/mapper/VG-data
